{"tid":1594697,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(預大量負皮) 聲底好只係你唱歌嘅先天優勢","createTime":"2019-09-25T16:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T03:21:19.000Z","uid":108894,"like":7,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d852bd1f93072ea4fde92f375ce4314c7d019c3f","tid":1594697,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"好多人好鍾意話聲底好至唱到好歌，我聽完即刻唔會再理呢個人嘅理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#by<br />\n<br />\n唱歌黎聲底好只係你先天優勢，如果你天生把聲真係好吸引人嘅，恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係聲底完全唔係唱歌好與壞嘅指標<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等於跑步時你起跑線前人地幾步，但係後面嘅人只要有適當嘅練習，完全有追上嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n一般人只要掌握到正確發聲技巧，學好樂理 (音樂感冇咁好嘅咪花多幾倍時間去tune自己個pitch) ，學識細心分析理解每一首歌嘅內在情感，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何</span></span></strong>一個人都可以唱好歌<br />\n<br />\n至於聲底就真係天生嘅，人地覺得難聽都冇辦法，你嘅聲音係無法改變，你無法期望個個鍾意你嘅聲，但係如果唱歌發聲正確，運氣正確身體同喉嚨放鬆，有用心去理解歌曲情感，有投入個心去唱，一定有人聽得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算容祖兒，陳奕迅，謝安琪，周杰倫呢D天皇天后一樣有人唔鍾意 (利申: 我正正唔太鍾意周杰倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n你無能力控制到人地覺得你把聲難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 唱歌難聽，大把野唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed94762a7debbd45db8477831bd5b854f256e95","tid":1594697,"uid":195904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"有啲人天生好好技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86986565ff10017ab79f337710849ddefac8dae7","tid":1594697,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aed94762a7debbd45db8477831bd5b854f256e95","tid":1594697,"uid":195904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"有啲人天生好好技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:42:44.000Z","msg":"呢D就係優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係都要經過訓練先能夠發揮出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dca8271c70fb38a1c164b30fc74715b7c321b58","tid":1594697,"uid":62376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"張學友話自己無學過唱歌"},{"pid":"9a063cd65d37d38ac86b772c92e03d1909bffe37","tid":1594697,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1dca8271c70fb38a1c164b30fc74715b7c321b58","tid":1594697,"uid":62376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"張學友話自己無學過唱歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:57:14.000Z","msg":"無學過＝/＝無練過把聲"},{"pid":"5c77b6e06634aecd2036ff34cc8c48b3b837ceba","tid":1594697,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":